Package: control-port-filter
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: tor
Depends: torsocks-remove-ld-preload, netcat-traditional, ucspi-tcp, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Filter for Tor control protocol commands
 Filters out Tor control protocol commands that are dangerous for anonymity
 such as GETINFO ADDRESS. Acts as a proxy between the client application and
 Tor.
